title: SFC bans Wong Sze Yiu for six months (SFC - Securities and Futures Commission)
text: ( Source : SFC - Securities and Futures Commission ) The Securities and Futures Commission (SFC) has banned Mr Wong Sze Yiu, a former account executive of Core Pacific-Yamaichi International ( H.K. ) Limited (CPYI), from re-entering the industry
